properties.description:
Bring Construct data to Consolidted DWH
for rewards project

source.sqlReaderQuery:
select a.RewardsProgramId,
	   a.RewardsProgramExternalId as KobieId,
	   a.StartDate,
	   a.EndDate,
	   b.ClientId,
	   b.ClientNumber,
	   c.RewardsProgramBINId,
           c.BIN,
	   c.[SourceCodeId],
           a.ProgramCode  
FROM [dbo].[RewardsPrograms] a
INNER JOIN [dbo].[RewardsConfiguration] b
	on a.[RewardsConfigurationId] = b.[RewardsConfigurationId]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[RewardsProgramBINs] c
	on a.RewardsProgramId = c.RewardsProgramId
where (A.EndDate IS NULL or A.EndDate >CAST(GETDATE()-1 AS DATE))
and  C.Status = 'A'
